Local  Integer  STAT, OK, I, WFLAG, WTYPMAJ, WOK_MAJENG
Local  Char     WCRIT_CHARGPWD(240)
Local  Integer  WNBPCE
Local  Integer  WRETOUR , WECRITURE, MAXI, TYPORG
Local  Char     COMPTA_CRIT(250)
Local  Char     WMESSAGE(250), WMSG(120)
Local  Libelle  NB_PWH, CREFLG
